			<div class="content" id="post-content-2472490">
									

<p>Great job TwistedGears, this gave me the Chiba City blues (in a good way).</p>
<p>Loved Navarro and the humor, and your writing really stood out, with bits such as &quot;Legs melting, he pressed onward&quot; contributing to the overall neo-noir/cyberpunk feel of the tale.</p>
